Position error and accuracy

PA

Predicted PA from the global model, namely the estimated mean PE including 95 % CI (and density distribution, only in middle and bottom panels) for all present combinations of Ac-Sc per site and method. For predictions, maxSig, (weight) and cover were set to their respective raw data mean per Ac-Sc combination.

PA50

Predicted PA50 from the global model, namely the estimated 50% quantile of PE including 95 % CI (and density distribution, only in middle and bottom panels) for all present combinations of Ac-Sc per site and method. For predictions, maxSig, (weight) and cover were set to their respective raw data mean per Ac-Sc combination.

PA65

Predicted PA65 from the global model, namely the estimated 65% quantile of PE including 95 % CI (and density distribution, only in middle and bottom panels) for all present combinations of Ac-Sc per site and method. For predictions, maxSig, (weight) and cover were set to their respective raw data mean per Ac-Sc combination.
